<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Binary_function on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/binary_function/</link><description>Recent content in Binary_function on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/binary_function/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>[Solution] C++ binary_function Deprecated — Replace with std::function</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/deprecated/cpp/binary_function/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/deprecated/cpp/binary_function/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="solution-c-binary_function-deprecated--replace-with-stdfunction"&gt;[Solution] C++ binary_function Deprecated — Replace with std::function&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;std::binary_function&lt;/code&gt; was deprecated in C++11 and removed in C++17 because it was an unnecessary base class for binary function objects. It provided &lt;code&gt;first_argument_type&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;second_argument_type&lt;/code&gt;, and &lt;code&gt;result_type&lt;/code&gt; typedefs that are no longer needed with modern C++.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="what-youll-see"&gt;What You&amp;rsquo;ll See&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In C++11/14:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;warning: &amp;#39;std::binary_function&amp;#39; is deprecated
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;In C++17:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;error: &amp;#39;binary_function&amp;#39; is not a member of &amp;#39;std&amp;#39;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="why-deprecated"&gt;Why Deprecated&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;std::binary_function&lt;/code&gt; was deprecated because:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Unnecessary base class&lt;/strong&gt;: Function objects don&amp;rsquo;t need a common base class.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;typedefs are obsolete&lt;/strong&gt;: Type traits can deduce argument and result types.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Lambdas are simpler&lt;/strong&gt;: No class definition needed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Prevents optimization&lt;/strong&gt;: Inheritance can inhibit compiler optimizations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="old-code-deprecated"&gt;Old Code (Deprecated)&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-cpp" data-lang="cpp"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;#include&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;&amp;lt;functional&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;#include&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;&amp;lt;algorithm&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;#include&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;&amp;lt;vector&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;#include&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;&amp;lt;iostream&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;struct&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Multiply&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; std&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;binary_function&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;int&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;int&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;int&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;operator&lt;/span&gt;()(&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; a, &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; b) &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; a &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt; b;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;};
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;main&lt;/span&gt;() {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; std&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;vector&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;int&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; nums &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; {&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;};
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; product &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; std&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;accumulate(nums.begin(), nums.end(), &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;, Multiply());
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; std&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;cout &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Product: &amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt; product &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt; std&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;endl;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="new-code--lambda-replacement"&gt;New Code — Lambda Replacement&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-cpp" data-lang="cpp"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;#include&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;&amp;lt;algorithm&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;#include&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;&amp;lt;vector&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;#include&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;&amp;lt;iostream&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;main&lt;/span&gt;() {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; std&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;vector&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;int&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; nums &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; {&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;};
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Lambda — no class definition needed
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; product &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; std&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;accumulate(nums.begin(), nums.end(), &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;,
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; [](&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; a, &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; b) { &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; a &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt; b; });
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; std&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;cout &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Product: &amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt; product &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt; std&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;endl;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="new-code--function-object-without-base-class"&gt;New Code — Function Object Without Base Class&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-cpp" data-lang="cpp"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;#include&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;&amp;lt;algorithm&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;#include&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;&amp;lt;vector&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;#include&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;&amp;lt;iostream&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Simple function object — no inheritance needed
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;struct&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Multiply&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;operator&lt;/span&gt;()(&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; a, &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; b) &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; a &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt; b;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;};
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;main&lt;/span&gt;() {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; std&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;vector&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;int&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; nums &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; {&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;};
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; product &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; std&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;accumulate(nums.begin(), nums.end(), &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;, Multiply());
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; std&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;cout &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Product: &amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt; product &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt; std&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;endl;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="migration-steps"&gt;Migration Steps&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Find all binary_function usage&lt;/strong&gt;:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;grep -rn &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;\bbinary_function\b&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; --include&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;*.h&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; --include&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;*.hpp&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; --include&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;*.cpp&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; /path/to/project/
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start="2"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Remove the inheritance&lt;/strong&gt;: &lt;code&gt;struct Func : public std::binary_function&amp;lt;T1, T2, R&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt; becomes &lt;code&gt;struct Func&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>